                <p>TED is a nonpartisan nonprofit devoted to spreading ideas, usually in the form of short, powerful talks.
                    TED began in 1984 as a conference where Technology, Entertainment and Design converged, and today covers
                    almost all topics — from science to business to global issues — in more than 110 languages. Meanwhile,
                    independently run TEDx events help share ideas in communities around the world. Ted Talks:
                    <a href="https://www.ted.com">https://www.ted.com</a>
                </p>
                </br>
                </br>© 2018 Copyright Ted Talk Scraper
                <a href="https://github.com/janetcushing">Janet Cushing</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>